{"tid":2295864,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[派仔是靚午]派克雞扒啊屌你老母","createTime":"2020-11-22T05:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T07:36:39.000Z","uid":230293,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c3880a9e798563b9f7a7ac8bc8d7f2b9eff687b","tid":2295864,"uid":230293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WrCZziD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrCZziD.jpg&h=ac401253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日樓豬為左開呢個Post特登行左廿分鐘去買塊G排<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個炸G排個台仔哥哥見到我，講左句&rdquo;幹又是你&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日冇乜人買，佢好好心機幫我炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外皮酥脆，入面舊G好Juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係食埋今次要減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7774bf9f32edb480bf3f928b164332ceb4cdcc0b","tid":2295864,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:31:51.000Z","msg":"想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b43c63f1233f444474c77de64be8193a13dc23","tid":2295864,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:45:52.000Z","msg":"係台灣定香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeaac6f61290de30d7fe91826a7c84617980e0fc","tid":2295864,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">炸雞巴啊</span>"},{"pid":"32741080e76e91c6